N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 163.14 - Auditing

State Regulations
A duly authorized representative of the Department of State
may audit any course, and may verify attendance and inspect the records of
attendance of the course at any time during its presentation or
thereafter. Notes
